{"tid":2353662,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朴軫永真的是好老闆！二話不說借錢給Rain媽媽看病，還取消行程送媽媽去醫院","createTime":"2021-01-05T02:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T04:40:36.000Z","uid":16659,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"489da6968b3d9b97208b8016ebac2a551c9f84bf","tid":2353662,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:20:00.000Z","msg":"當時Rain還是高中生，四處求助卻屢屢碰壁的聖誕佳節，只有朴軫永一個人向他伸出援手...... T^T<br />\n<br />\n上週末播出的SBS綜藝節目《我家的熊孩子》里，Rain分享了自己人生中3個最重要的機會，其中第一個就是「遇見朴軫永」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_84a359061f3d8a121db22c5454c9b5ed/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-04/132772-891822.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_84a359061f3d8a121db22c5454c9b5ed%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-04%2F132772-891822.png&h=01bd649c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家也許都已經知道，Rain小時候家境非常不好，父親生意失敗、無奈之下獨自出國打工，媽媽則因為積勞成疾患上糖尿病，生活的重擔全都落到還在讀中學的Rain身上。因為窮，Rain曾經一套運動服穿了六七個月，甚至因此患上皮膚病。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_94444e130c6dd943ec42d7b05832831d/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-04/132772-891831.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_94444e130c6dd943ec42d7b05832831d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-04%2F132772-891831.jpeg&h=d0248978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「那是97年、98年左右，媽媽沒錢去醫院，我到處求助但是沒有一個人肯幫忙。 其實只要去醫院媽媽就能多活一段時間。 當時是聖誕前一天，我打電話給朴軫永說，哥，救救我們吧，媽媽沒有看病的錢，沒辦法去醫院。 」當時Rain只有17歲，就算想貸款都沒辦法做擔保，真的是走投無路。<br />\n<br />\n朴軫永得知之後立即取消所有行程開車來到Rain家裡，這才知道Rain家的狀況這麼艱難。 「朴軫永和我一起把媽媽背上車去了醫院，還簽了擔保書讓媽媽住院，媽媽因此得以多活了兩三周時間。 」<br />\n<br />\nRain說：「最近和軫永哥在練習間隙吃飯時，我還在對他說，謝謝你讓我能夠吃飯和生活。 小時候看到朋友去披薩店買披薩都覺得好羨慕。 還有那種家庭餐廳，看到別人家開著漂亮的車子、穿得暖暖的，小朋友拉著爸媽的手一起走進去吃飯，我都會想：這是什麼樣的福氣啊？ 我真的太難了。 而那個時候拉住我的手的，就是軫永哥。 」<br />\n<br />\n再一次感到「大猩猩」很帥氣XD<br />\n<br />\n熬過那段辛苦的時光，現在的Rain單是房地產就超過450億韓元，人生真的發生翻天覆地的改變！<br />\n<br />\n這段往事每次都讓人看到淚目，朴軫永真的是Rain的貴人，希望大家以後的人生也都只有幸福啊~<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eHhSDLwyvcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeHhSDLwyvcg&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=b1cf1366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eHhSDLwyvcg</a>"},{"pid":"a4ac3704e35927f6cf1bf65cf28c22b5a922598d","tid":2353662,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"爸爸..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1cb4b74e17c5a723d7abde1244b5a2b76bf3f5","tid":2353662,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4ac3704e35927f6cf1bf65cf28c22b5a922598d","tid":2353662,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"爸爸..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"我愛Daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089f3bb90b87b97a60c6532c377667c9723a5bcf","tid":2353662,"uid":81486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"哭能左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />JYB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7509632862854c6b16eabcfb6ca858b9be4dd1","tid":2353662,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"089f3bb90b87b97a60c6532c377667c9723a5bcf","tid":2353662,"uid":81486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"哭能左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />JYB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"JYP Daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440a3723f62