"quote":{"pid":"91acdd5018f8801875ef602f19a4c3560bf200a1","tid":2353662,"uid":277816,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c08849eceb8a45358aec6ff69a1917caf29b9b0b","tid":2353662,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3241a2cc346b08d41f63509023be551921afa44","tid":2353662,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"迫子瑜道歉<br />\n好老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"偽君子?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"應該係子瑜媽媽逼子瑜道歉（當期時子瑜媽媽飛去韓國），因為JYP Entertainment 已出道歉文。可能子瑜媽媽覺得子瑜將來會去支那發展。<br />\n<br />\n之後，JYP無為錢安排Twice去支那出道，而且一直無去台灣演出同開演唱會（廢事小粉紅又話有差別），所以Twice出道至今都無去中台兩地，JYP都無話為錢而廢，世界市場何其大，美日就係第一同第二大嘅市場，唔使低頭。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"sm就低晒頭啦&hellip;一隊新女團搞衰晒幾十年基業"},{"pid":"c5a935bbc51647e05c4b66952ff08226e4e77d7f","tid":2353662,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91acdd5018f8801875ef602f19a4c3560bf200a1","tid":2353662,"uid":277816,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c08849eceb8a45358aec6ff69a1917caf29b9b0b","tid":2353662,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3241a2cc346b08d41f63509023be551921afa44","tid":2353662,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"迫子瑜道歉<br />\n好老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"偽君子?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"應該係子瑜媽媽逼子瑜道歉（當期時子瑜媽媽飛去韓國），因為JYP Entertainment 已出道歉文。可能子瑜媽媽覺得子瑜將來會去支那發展。<br />\n<br />\n之後，JYP無為錢安排Twice去支那出道，而且一直無去台灣演出同開演唱會（廢事小粉紅又話有差別），所